1. hadoop -jar jarname classname argument1 argument2
2. pass argument 1 as input file path
3. pass argument 2 as output path
4. Pass the input and output arguments as arguments  for Invertedindex.java file
5. It will compute the inverted index for given arguments
6. It will create the output folder and inverted index folder inside that particular folder 
7. output file in which key as word and list of all document titles.